{"tid":947083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洗衣店貓隻跳入洗衣機亡　店主伸手救貓致骨折","createTime":"2018-12-19T04:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T04:34:59.000Z","uid":6497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c611e0a017c09f7cb2bd626592de9a16c1516734","tid":947083,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181219/s00001/a9287782c3610b8a980e5c6189f156c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181219%2Fs00001%2Fa9287782c3610b8a980e5c6189f156c6.jpg&h=a76fc469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元朗有女子意外受傷。凌晨零時許，元朗屏會街1-25號一間洗衣店的57歲鄧姓女店主，工作期間發現其中一隻所飼養的貓，意外跳進一部運作中的洗衣機。鄧救貓心切，左手伸進洗衣機後受傷骨折，她其後自行弄停洗衣機並報警。<br />\n<br />\n人員接報到場，鄧清醒送往屯門醫院治理。該貓隻由消防取出後，證實死亡。據悉，洗衣機為一部約3呎高、直徑2呎的滾筒式洗衣機，事發時機門未關上，鄧於店內同時飼養其他貓隻。<br />\n<br />\n警方初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，案件列作「有人意外受傷 &ndash; 工業意外」。"},{"pid":"8eef32e52315245b13d36d3ff662f1773f2ec8f7","tid":947083,"uid":69886,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:07:40.000Z","msg":"死傻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09e604976ea52c11e432552c5cb1d6990e5d89c","tid":947083,"uid":28913,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:07:45.000Z","msg":"冷靜d, 停左機先嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608d987d011c731eaa652d0e8b4a06ab7ef016c3","tid":947083,"uid":107364,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:08:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4d389e7883ab8b1b1ae08314e690970bf815b9e","tid":947083,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨左部機先唔得"},{"pid":"ae4c34f0630826551bd07cdff05c12f4097a910e","tid":947083,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:11:44.000Z","msg":"原來仲有人用緊冇蓋/打開左蓋仲郁嘅機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea4c08628cf36be6f66118e446d11ffc8828c11","tid":947083,"uid":19990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:14:58.000Z","msg":"RIP 貓貓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n店主都好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb21d8e176ffed314adc7c15a6fbd82553a9c143","tid":947083,"uid":34466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"隻貓必死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算熄咗機都有排完全停定<br />\n只能怪自己無閂好害死隻貓"},{"pid":"fe38b2ac43812fc578c18df245f2ea909b930bf1","tid":947083,"uid":106426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:34:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}